This repository provides a from-scratch Rust implementation of the Firecracker
Go SDK layout and behavior.

The crate interacts with the public Firecracker API and uses the Firecracker Go
SDK as a behavior and repository-shape reference during migration work. Rust
source files in this repository are intended to be authored directly for this
crate rather than copied from sibling Rust SDK repositories.
